social_posts.post_text: Yes, there will be dancing!! We are hosting our first ever private NYE soirée and you are all invited!! My pal DJ @kellycoleusa will be spinning til 2am so swipe thru for more info! Make your reservations at @theorbar or go to  http://www.theorbar.com/store-2/p/new-years-eve. Hope to see you!!! xx

Santa came to my bar @theorbar last night and he’s got some moves!!!! MERRY CHRISTMAS EVERYONE!! Love you all!!
🎅🏼: @007grady
📸: @yasueinparadise
Happy New Year!!! Wishing you all good health, happiness, peace and prosperity in the new year…..and beyond!! Love you!!
Me cos our baby @orbarweho is FINALLY open!!!

I’ll be at my glamorous new @orbarweho tonight with Iris if anyone wants to join me. Actually, Iris is not only the name of this ADORABLE little pooch but also the name of our top-selling drink! So come have an Iris with me, but not with Iris cos she is busy tonight with her dad (and Or Bar co-owner) @robnovinger. Cheers and Happy Friday!!!🍸🐶 🌸
📸: @chelsealaurenla
Suited up for the @marantzofficial x @maxrichtermusic #marantzcinemanights at the epic #lautner #sheatsgoldsteinresidence. Great night surrounded by super sexy audio and architecture.

Love IS the drug so whether you’re single, married, dating, uncoupled, polyamorous, asexual, friends with benefits, etc. Valentine’s day is for EVERYONE! So come take back V-Day with me at @orbarweho!!! xx
Truly fabulous and a real star. I was lucky enough to style her in the second to last pic. She was a bad ass in her 70s!!!!! RIP Raquel Welch. 💔
Just sitting at my @orbarweho and a customer left this behind. Thank you @dustymillerart for the sneak attack portrait! You made my day!
Festive Cocktail Attire Louque requested & served. @glaad awards

@lalgbtcenter #centergala last night. Attire was “cocktail fabulous” and it was HOT outside. This is a gorgeous @ports1961 suit from about 10 yrs ago and I made it into shorts because why not? I love shopping my closet. @wolkmorais tie, @louboutinworld kicks and @dockerskhakis shirt (w the sleeves cut off cos again, it was hot lol). Check out my story to see what it looked like before. 😁

Me and my crew at the @dailyfrontrow LA Fashion Awards wearing @etro blazer, @lanvin pants, 
@commedesgarcons shoes and a #neckmess of fantastic gold chains from @lagos_jewelry

Reposting from @orbarweho one of the art pieces I curated. Check out @samuelhatmaker ’s work with #legos!
…
…
@samuelhatmaker is one local #lgbtqartist whose original pieces grace the walls at Or Bar. Sam’s work with #legos is mostly fun and pop — like this amazing #DonnaSummer ❤️ — but we wanted something a bit more naughty for the bar. Can you guess the subject of Sam’s piece on slide 2? If not, come to the bar and find out! Thank you Sam!!!!

Unintentional French Riviera vibes in @tods shoes, #vintage @paulsmithdesign pants and @hm stripes. Big thanks to @apaigemueller & @solawave for the happy hour travel talk with @cris_flyer & @atwjustin. 📸 by @earthalchemist with backseat creative direction by @arubey 😉.

Join me in supporting the Elton John AIDS Foundation to promote global health equity and finally end AIDS for all. I must admit, it wasn’t too hard for me to find my inner Elton, but how about you?? Share a photo of how you let your #InnerElton out and tag @ejaf. 
Join us to end AIDS forever. For more information go to link in bio or
